洗石庵有庵门、经堂、佛堂三进堂，为广西境内保存最完整、最华丽的寺庙之一。经堂为三开间，屋顶为金色琉璃硬山重檐。佛堂为三开间大殿，外檐为石柱、内为红漆木柱、下为宝瓶型石柱<ref name="A" />。庵前有唐建李公祠。庵后有清建的[[龙华寺|龙华寺]]及李宗仁飞阁。还有[[乳泉|乳泉]]、[[史隐洞|史隐洞]]等<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://spot.cnair.com/guangxi/guiping/list_xishian.htm |title=洗石庵 |access-date=2009-09-03 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307055132/http://spot.cnair.com/guangxi/guiping/list_xishian.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 佛事活动 ==
洗石庵每年都举办“浴佛节”，即每年农历四月初八，纪念佛陀[[释迦牟尼|释迦牟尼]]诞辰<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gx.xinhuanet.com/dtzx/2009-05/05/content_16431916.htm |title=桂平西山浴佛文化旅游节盛况空前 |access-date=2009-09-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304122010/http://www.gx.xinhuanet.com/dtzx/2009-05/05/content_16431916.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20090501/newgx49fb124e-2028729.shtml |title=桂平"浴佛节"隆重开幕 千人朝拜上山 |access-date=2009-09-03 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605164328/http://www.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20090501/newgx49fb124e-2028729.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.dayoo.com/society/57401/200905/03/57401_5856198.htm |title=广西桂平“浴佛节”大典吸引数万人观礼 |access-date=2009-09-03 |archive-date=2015-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512163639/http://news.dayoo.com/society/57401/200905/03/57401_5856198.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年，“浴佛节”进行传灯祈愿[[汶川大地震|四川地震]]遇难亡灵<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20090501/newgx49fb124e-2028714.shtml |title=“浴佛节”传灯祈愿 虔诚祈福“5·12” |access-date=2009-09-03 |archive-date=2019-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602123138/http://news.gxnews.com.cn/staticpages/20090501/newgx49fb124e-2028714.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

